<li class='cover' id='bookCover_6623920'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6623920-the-dead-hand"><img alt="The Dead Hand: The Untold Story of the Cold War Arms Race and its Dangerous Legacy" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320419175l/6623920._SX98_.jpg" />
