<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/52047702-kim-jong-un-and-the-bomb"><img alt="Kim Jong Un and the Bomb: Survival and Deterrence in North Korea" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1571686718l/52047702._SX98_SY160_.jpg" />
