<li class='cover' id='bookCover_10859327'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/10859327-money-and-power"><img alt="Money and Power: How Goldman Sachs Came to Rule the World" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320518705l/10859327._SX98_.jpg" />
