          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/10263.Richard_Rhodes"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1445446336p3/10263.jpg);'></div>
